As y’all already know that @geetanjalistudioofficial is finally open here in Hisar 🤩 I went there to get lil pampered with my friends 💆‍♀️ but after a great consultation session with the experts I ended up getting my hair colour done the very same day and it turned out amazing. 😍 All thanks to the hairstylist, I trusted him and went for a bold colour this time and I totally loved the results ❤️✨ Subtle yet very stylish 🥵🔥
Loved the services, interior and hospitality 🙌✨
Highly Recommended 🔥🔥
